realme GT 2 Pro 5G 256GB Benchmark Scores Overview

realme GT 2 Pro 5G 256GB is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 1. The processor is Octa core (3 GHz, Single core, Cortex X2 + 2.5 GHz, Tri core, Cortex A710 + 1.8 GHz, Quad core, Cortex A510) that uses 64 bit architecture and Adreno 730 GPU. It runs on Android v12 operating system with 12 GB RAM and 256 GB ROM.

realme GT 2 Pro 5G 256GB AnTuTu Score:

realme GT 2 Pro 5G 256GB has an overall AnTuTu score of 933,319. The benchmark app also gives individual scores for CPU, Memory, GPU, and UX tests. realme GT 2 Pro 5G 256GB scored 216,347 for CPU, 161,259 for Memory, 394,515 for GPU, and 161,198 for UX test.
